{"title": "Red, green or blue tiles", "body": "<div class=\"problem_content\" role=\"problem\">\n<p>A row of five black square tiles is to have a number of its tiles replaced with coloured oblong tiles chosen from red (length two), green (length three), or blue (length four).</p>\n<p>If red tiles are chosen there are exactly seven ways this can be done.</p>\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\"><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#cc0000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"44\"/></td>\n<td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n<td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n<td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n</tr></table></td>\n<td>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\"><tr><td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#cc0000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"44\"/></td>\n<td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n<td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n</tr></table></td>\n<td>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\"><tr><td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n<td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#cc0000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"44\"/></td>\n<td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n</tr></table></td>\n<td>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\"><tr><td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n<td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n<td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#cc0000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"44\"/></td>\n</tr></table></td>\n</tr><tr><td>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\"><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#cc0000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"44\"/></td>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#cc0000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"44\"/></td>\n<td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n</tr></table></td>\n<td>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\"><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#cc0000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"44\"/></td>\n<td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#cc0000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"44\"/></td>\n</tr></table></td>\n<td>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\"><tr><td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#cc0000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"44\"/></td>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#cc0000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"44\"/></td>\n</tr></table></td>\n<td>\u00a0</td>\n</tr></table><p>If green tiles are chosen there are three ways.</p>\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\"><tr><td colspan=\"3\" style=\"background-color:#00cc00;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"68\"/></td>\n<td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n<td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n</tr></table></td>\n<td>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\"><tr><td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"background-color:#00cc00;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"68\"/></td>\n<td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n</tr></table></td>\n<td>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\"><tr><td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n<td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"background-color:#00cc00;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"68\"/></td>\n</tr></table></td>\n<td>\u00a0</td>\n</tr></table><p>And if blue tiles are chosen there are two ways.</p>\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\"><tr><td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n<td colspan=\"4\" style=\"background-color:#0000cc;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"92\"/></td>\n</tr></table></td>\n<td>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"2\"><tr><td colspan=\"4\" style=\"background-color:#0000cc;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"92\"/></td>\n<td style=\"background-color:#000000;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"20\" src=\"images/spacer.gif\" width=\"20\"/></td>\n</tr></table></td>\n</tr></table><p>Assuming that colours cannot be mixed there are 7 + 3 + 2 = 12 ways of replacing the black tiles in a row measuring five units in length.</p>\n<p>How many different ways can the black tiles in a row measuring fifty units in length be replaced if colours cannot be mixed and at least one coloured tile must be used?</p>\n<p class=\"note\">NOTE: This is related to <a href=\"problem=117\">Problem 117</a>.</p>\n</div>"}